ttp_template:
<group name="failover_active_last_failover_date_last_failover_reason_last_failover_time">
Device Priority  : {{PRIORITY | ORPHRASE}}
Failover {{STATE | ORPHRASE}}  : {{FAILOVER_ACTIVE | ORPHRASE}}
Peer State  : {{PEER_STATE | ORPHRASE}}
Last Failover  : {{LAST_FAILOVER_DATE | re("[\\d\\.\\(\\)A-Za-z]+")}} {{LAST_FAILOVER_TIME | ORPHRASE}}
Last Failover Reason  : {{LAST_FAILOVER_REASON | ORPHRASE}}
Uptime (days)  : {{UPTIME_DAYS | ORPHRASE}}
</group>
cli_content:
High Availability State
------------------------
Device Priority       : 200
Failover Active       : Yes
State                 : Active
Peer State            : Standby
Last Failover         : 2023-10-05 14:23:19
Last Failover Reason  : Link Failure
Uptime (days)         : 15
textfsm_template:
Value PRIORITY (\d+)
Value FAILOVER_ACTIVE (Yes|No)
Value STATE (\S+)
Value PEER_STATE (\S+)
Value LAST_FAILOVER_DATE (\d{4}-\d{2}-\d{2})
Value LAST_FAILOVER_TIME (\d{2}:\d{2}:\d{2})
Value LAST_FAILOVER_REASON (.*)
Value UPTIME_DAYS (\d+)

Start
  ^\s*Device Priority\s+:\s+${PRIORITY}\s*$$
  ^\s*Failover Active\s+:\s+${FAILOVER_ACTIVE}\s*$$
  ^\s*State\s+:\s+${STATE}\s*$$
  ^\s*Peer State\s+:\s+${PEER_STATE}\s*$$
  ^\s*Last Failover\s+:\s+${LAST_FAILOVER_DATE}\s+${LAST_FAILOVER_TIME}\s*$$
  ^\s*Last Failover Reason\s+:\s+${LAST_FAILOVER_REASON}\s*$$
  ^\s*Uptime \(days\)\s+:\s+${UPTIME_DAYS}\s*$$ -> Record
